		<title>Addressing Hurdles in DOGE&#058; Challenges of Dogecoin Governance</title>
		<link>https://securenest.org/learn/dogecoin-governance-challenges</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jordan Adams]]></dc:creator>
