<p>The BIP process is a structured way for developers to present improvements, ranging from consensus-critical changes to informational updates. Dogecoin, though inspired by the playful Shiba Inu meme, takes its governance cues from such rigorous frameworks, ensuring that any alterations to the protocol are meticulously scrutinized and broadly agreed upon.</p>



