<li><strong>Development Hierarchy</strong>: Core developers wield significant influence over dogecoin governance, prioritizing certain upgrades or improvements which may not align with the wider community&#8217;s desires.</li>
</ul>



<p><strong>Power Concentration:</strong></p>



<ul>
