<li><strong>Mining Pools</strong>: Control over hash power centralizes dogecoin governance implicitly, as major mining pools have a larger say in consensus-related decisions.</li>
</ul>



<p>Your role as part of the dogecoin governance landscape is to navigate these limitations, advocate for transparent decision-making processes, and strive for a balance of power that reflects the community&#8217;s ethos.</p>



